data.description:
Spacious, end-unit townhome with 1-car garage and driveway parking space. Exterior upgrades completed in Oct 2023 include new vinyl siding, windows, sliding glass door, and gutters. Well maintained interior with refreshed interior paint, upgraded laminate wood-grain finished flooring in living space, upgraded lighting throughout, and new carpet upstairs. New dishwasher, refrigerator, washer and dryer. A/C unit installed Nov 2021, wired for security. 

Enjoy backyard preserve views and club pool in the community. Great home to live in or to purchase as an investment property. 

Seller is motivated, schedule a showing today!
